abstract: >-
  VEHRON is a modular, BEV-focused prescribed-speed vehicle simulation
  framework for deterministic energy, thermal-trend, and battery
  stress-history studies under configurable duty cycles and operating
  conditions, with packaged WLTP Class 3b and MIDC benchmark workflows.
keywords:
  - vehicle simulation
  - battery electric vehicle
  - BEV
  - battery stress history
  - thermal modeling
  - drive cycle
url: "https://vehron.org"
repository-code: "https://github.com/vehron-dev/vehron"
license-url: "https://www.gnu.org/licenses/agpl-3.0.txt"
